<TITLE> BKSP get-together on Friday </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, April 16 (bdnews24.com)  A grand get-together of former BKSP students will be held at its campus in Savar on Friday. The programme includes a colourful rally, followed by audio-visual presentation of memories of the BKSP students and recollection by ex-students, officials, teachers and coaches. All donations will be handed over for treatment of Barkat, a BKSP gymnastics student who has been paralysed following a training accident. The programme will be rounded off by a musical session. The Bangladesh Krira Shikka Protisthan, the country's lone sports institute, has produced numerous quality sportsmen and women in its 23-year history. bd
